metadata.name: Silver Mint Pass #1
metadata.description:
This Silver pass is your ticket to the 'World of Godard'. This NFT doesn't expire and can be connected to your account at nft.MichaelGodard.com to unlock physical & digital perks, including early access to select projects, real life experiences and limited edition works.

---------

Visit the official site: https://nft.michaelgodard.com/
